OL,5, The United Nations head has strongly   
OL,6, condemned a Taliban ban on Afghan women
OL,7, working for the organisation.          
OL,9,FSecretary General Antonio Guterres     
OL,10,Fdemanded Afghanistan's rulers          
OL,11,Fimmediately revoke the order, saying it
OL,12,Fwas discriminatory and breached        
OL,13,Finternational human rights law.        
OL,15,FFemale staff were "essential for UN    
OL,16,Foperations" in the country, he said.   
OL,18,FThe Taliban have increasingly          
OL,19,Frestricted women's freedoms since      
OL,20,Fseizing power in 2021.                 
